IN THE BACK OF MY CAR.

242
00:14:09,681 --> 00:14:10,682
I'M WORKING.

243
00:14:10,682 --> 00:14:12,184
GABY, LISTEN,
MAYBE WHEN THE SHIFT'S OVER,

244
00:14:12,184 --> 00:14:13,685
I'LL CALL YOU,
WHATEVER.

245
00:14:14,186 --> 00:14:15,687
WE'LL GO OUT, WE'LL GRAB
A BITE OR SOMETHING, OK?

246
00:14:15,687 --> 00:14:16,688
[BEEPING]

247
00:14:16,688 --> 00:14:18,690
LOOK, THAT'S MY DISPATCHER.
I GOT TO GO.

248
00:14:18,690 --> 00:14:19,858
I GOT TO GO, BYE.

249
00:14:22,694 --> 00:14:24,696
YEAH, IT'S 4 UNDERWAY.

250
00:14:24,696 --> 00:14:26,698
Dispatcher: AFTER THE DROP,
CAN YOU SWING A PICKUP
AT THE STANHOPE?

251
00:14:26,698 --> 00:14:29,701
LADY NAMED EASTERN
ASKED FOR YOU.

252
00:14:30,202 --> 00:14:33,205
EASTERN? EASTERN? UH, YEAH.
WHERE'S THE DROP AT?

253
00:14:33,205 --> 00:14:34,706
SHE DIDN'T SAY.

254
00:14:36,875 --> 00:14:39,094
[MAN AND WOMAN MOANING]

255
00:14:44,599 --> 00:14:46,718
[BREAKS SCREECHING]

256
00:14:47,135 --> 00:14:49,221
Man in back seat:
FUCK!

257
00:14:49,221 --> 00:14:52,724
I APOLOGIZE FOR
THE SUDDEN STOP, FOLKS,

258
00:14:52,724 --> 00:14:54,726
BUT HOPEFULLY
YOU WERE BELTED IN.

259
00:15:13,245 --> 00:15:15,747
OK. HERE WE ARE.

260
00:15:15,747 --> 00:15:19,251
HERE, TAKE THAT.

261
00:15:19,251 --> 00:15:20,752
PLEASURE SERVING YOU
AS ALWAYS, MR. HALLMAN.

262
00:15:20,752 --> 00:15:23,138
[CLEARS THROAT]

263
00:15:25,257 --> 00:15:26,758
[TELEPHONE BEEPS]

264
00:15:30,145 --> 00:15:31,763
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

265
00:15:34,266 --> 00:15:35,767
THIS IS RAVITCH.

266
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:37,269
HEY, IT'S SHERIFF.

267
00:15:37,269 --> 00:15:39,771
LISTEN, HOW MUCH IS
NEW YORK'S MOST FAMOUS
DIVORCE ATTORNEY WORTH TO YOU?

268
00:15:40,188 --> 00:15:42,274
HE'S WORTH SQUAT,
BROTHER. I'M SINGLE.

269
00:15:42,274 --> 00:15:45,277
UH, WHAT ABOUT
IF HE'S OUT BOINKING
AND GETTING BOMBED

270
00:15:45,277 --> 00:15:46,778
AND HIS WIFE'S
NOT WITH HIM?

271
00:15:47,028 --> 00:15:49,281
THAT'S A DIFFERENT STORY.

272
00:15:49,281 --> 00:15:51,283
RAVITCH, CAN'T YOU
FIND ANOTHER DESK?

273
00:15:51,783 --> 00:15:52,784
I'D SAY TWO BILLS.

274
00:15:53,084 --> 00:15:55,754
YOU'RE A CHEAP SON OF A BITCH.
GRAB A PEN.

275
00:15:55,837 --> 00:15:59,341
I'M SORRY.
OK, GIVE HER TO ME.

276
00:16:11,102 --> 00:16:12,103
THANK YOU.

277
00:16:29,620 --> 00:16:31,622
WE HEADED ANYWHERE
IN PARTICULAR?

278
00:16:31,705 --> 00:16:34,125
HOW ABOUT WE JUST
DRIVE AROUND THE PARK
FOR A LITTLE BIT?

279
00:16:34,542 --> 00:16:37,328
YOU GOT IT.
AROUND THE PARK.

280
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:41,632
I KNOW I HAVEN'T
DRIVEN YOU BEFORE.

281
00:16:41,632 --> 00:16:42,633
I NEVER FORGET
A FACE.

282
00:16:44,135 --> 00:16:46,137
HEY, DO YOU MIND
IF I SMOKE IN THE CAR?

283
00:16:46,253 --> 00:16:49,140
IT'S THE ONLY PLACE
IN TOWN LEFT THAT
YOU CAN SMOKE.

284
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:50,141
GO AHEAD.

285
00:16:52,643 --> 00:16:55,146
SO, UH,
WHO RECOMMENDED ME,
MISS EASTERN?

286
00:16:55,646 --> 00:16:56,647
PLEASE CALL ME BETH.

287
00:16:57,097 --> 00:17:00,184
OK, WHO RECOMMENDED
ME,BETH?

288
00:17:01,652 --> 00:17:03,154
LEWIS McBRIDE.

289
00:17:03,654 --> 00:17:04,655
LEW?

290
00:17:04,655 --> 00:17:05,656
WHAT DID HE SAY?

291
00:17:06,157 --> 00:17:07,658
"LOOK UP OLD SHERIFF
WHEN YOU GOT TO TOWN?"

292
00:17:07,658 --> 00:17:10,661
HOW DID YOU KNOW
WHERE TO FIND ME?

293
00:17:10,661 --> 00:17:13,664
LEW SAID YOU LIVED
IN BROOKLYN,

294
00:17:14,165 --> 00:17:15,666
ODDS WERE YOU WOULD BE
IN THE BOOK.

295
00:17:15,666 --> 00:17:17,168
YEAH, HUH?

296
00:17:17,168 --> 00:17:19,170
AND ODDS WERE
THAT I'D PROBABLY STILL
BE STUCK IN BROOKLYN,

297
00:17:19,170 --> 00:17:23,174
WHICH, YOU KNOW,
OBVIOUSLY I AM.

298
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:25,176
SO WHERE IS LEW, HUH?
IS HE IN TOWN HERE?

299
00:17:25,176 --> 00:17:31,182
SHERIFF, THE DAY YOU
AND TONY LEFT PANANG,

300
00:17:31,682 --> 00:17:34,018
A MAN CAME LOOKING
FOR A BIKE YOU GUYS
HAD RENTED.

301
00:17:35,686 --> 00:17:37,688
HE BROUGHT THE POLICE.

302
00:17:38,138 --> 00:17:39,690
ONLY THEY DIDN'T
FIND THE BIKE.

303
00:17:39,690 --> 00:17:42,193
THEY DID FIND
104 GRAMS OF HASHISH.

304
00:17:42,693 --> 00:17:46,697
SOME STASHED IN THE HUT,
SOME IN THE TRASH.

305
00:17:46,697 --> 00:17:48,199
JESUS CHRIST.

306
00:17:48,199 --> 00:17:52,203
AND LEWIS...CAUGHT HELL
FOR THAT, HUH?

307
00:17:52,403 --> 00:17:55,706
WELL, YEAH. HE SPENT
THE LAST TWO YEARS
IN PRISON.

308
00:17:55,706 --> 00:17:59,210
OH, MY GOD,
JESUS CHRIST.

309
00:17:59,210 --> 00:18:01,212
WHAT A NIGHTMARE
THAT MUST BE, HUH?

310
00:18:01,462 --> 00:18:05,216
IS HE STILL
IN PRISON NOW?

311
00:18:05,216 --> 00:18:07,668
FOR 8 MORE DAYS, YEAH.

312
00:18:07,751 --> 00:18:10,721
I MEAN, I WISH I WOULD
HAVE KNOWN SOONER.

313
00:18:10,721 --> 00:18:13,224
I MEAN, I DON'T KNOW
IF I COULD HAVE DONE
ANYTHING, BUT...

314
00:18:13,224 --> 00:18:14,725
AT LEAST HE'S
GETTING OUT IN 8 DAYS,
THOUGH, HUH?

315
00:18:14,725 --> 00:18:16,727
THAT'S, UH,
NOT THE CASE.

316
00:18:17,094 --> 00:18:20,231
IN MALAYSIA, ANYBODY
FOUND WITH MORE THAN
100 GRAMS OF HASHISH

317
00:18:20,231 --> 00:18:21,732
IS CONSIDERED
TO BE TRAFFICKING.

318
00:18:21,732 --> 00:18:22,733
TRAFFICKING?

319
00:18:22,733 --> 00:18:25,236
WHAT, IS THAT
LIKE DEALING?

320
00:18:25,236 --> 00:18:26,237
SHERIFF,

321
00:18:26,437 --> 00:18:32,243
IN ORDER FOR LEWIS NOT
TO BE CONSIDERED A DEALER,

322
00:18:32,243 --> 00:18:34,245
YOU AND TONY HAVE TO
FLY BACK TO PANANG

323
00:18:34,245 --> 00:18:36,747
AND ACCEPT YOUR SHARE
OF THE RESPONSIBILITY.

324
00:18:40,367 --> 00:18:43,254
AND WHAT ABOUT
ME AND TONY?
WHAT HAPPENS TO US?

325
00:18:43,254 --> 00:18:46,257
WELL, THE DEAL WAS THAT
IF BOTH OF YOU GO BACK,

326
00:18:46,757 --> 00:18:48,759
IT'S 3 YEARS APIECE.

327
00:18:48,759 --> 00:18:51,262
AND IF ONLY ONE OF YOU
GOES BACK, IT'S 6.

328
00:18:51,762 --> 00:18:52,263
WAIT, WAIT,
WAIT, WAIT. HOLD ON.

329
00:18:52,763 --> 00:18:54,265
IT'S 3? IT'S 6?

330
00:18:54,265 --> 00:18:56,267
WHY DON'T YOU FINISH
THAT SENTENCE FOR ME,
PLEASE?

331
00:18:56,267 --> 00:19:00,104
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT
3 YEARS IN PRISON, LADY,
6 YEARS IN PRISON.

332
00:19:00,104 --> 00:19:01,772
SHERIFF, LET ME MAKE
THIS CLEAR TO YOU.

333
00:19:02,273 --> 00:19:04,275
IN MALAYSIA,
DEALERS GET DEATH.

334
00:19:04,275 --> 00:19:07,278
JESUS CHRIST,
FOR A SHITTY BRICK
OF HASH?

335
00:19:07,278 --> 00:19:09,280
YOU'RE TELLING ME
IN 8 DAYS FROM NOW...

336
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:13,284
LEWIS McBRIDE
IS GOING TO HANG.

337
00:19:23,794 --> 00:19:25,796
WHAT ARE YOU?
HIS LAWYER?

338
00:19:25,796 --> 00:19:29,800
I'M HIS
AMERICAN LAWYER, YEAH.

339
00:19:45,316 --> 00:19:46,817
SO, HOW ABOUT
WE HAVE DINNER

340
00:19:46,817 --> 00:19:48,319
AND TALK MORE
ABOUT THIS?

341
00:19:48,319 --> 00:19:50,821
UH, CAN'T.
I'M ON UNTIL 2:00,
BUT THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

342
00:19:51,322 --> 00:19:52,823
DRINKS, THEN?

343
00:19:52,823 --> 00:19:55,326
WHAT? AT 2:00?
DON'T YOU SLEEP?

344
00:19:55,326 --> 00:19:57,328
WELL, I WANT TO
DO THIS MORE.

345
00:19:57,328 --> 00:19:58,329
BREAKFAST?

346
00:19:58,329 --> 00:19:59,330
CAN'T.

347
00:19:59,330 --> 00:20:00,331
LUNCH?

348
00:20:00,331 --> 00:20:01,332
I PULLED
A DAY SHIFT...

349
00:20:01,332 --> 00:20:02,333
ALL RIGHT.
BETH, I CAN'T...

350
00:20:02,333 --> 00:20:03,334
LET'S HAVE DINNER,
THEN.

351
00:20:03,334 --> 00:20:06,837
TOMORROW NIGHT,
HERE, SAY, 7:00?

352
00:20:07,338 --> 00:20:08,839
TOMORROW AT 7:00.

353
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:10,341
THANKS.

354
00:20:10,341 --> 00:20:11,342
THANKS.

355
00:20:50,381 --> 00:20:52,383
[DOOR UNLOCKING]

356
00:20:52,383 --> 00:20:53,884
[MAN SPEAKING MALAY]

357
00:21:10,768 --> 00:21:12,903
[CAR HORNS HONK]

358
00:21:21,912 --> 00:21:24,415
EXCUSE ME, I'M LOOKING
FOR TONY CROFT.

359
00:21:24,415 --> 00:21:25,916
YEAH, HE'S UP TOP.

360
00:21:25,916 --> 00:21:27,117
THANKS.

361
00:21:38,429 --> 00:21:41,932
Beth: SO, IF YOU DON'T
GO BACK, TONY,

362
00:21:42,299 --> 00:21:44,435
LEWIS WILL HANG.

363
00:21:48,439 --> 00:21:49,440
I'M SORRY.

364
00:21:51,942 --> 00:21:54,445
YOU JUST CAN'T COME
OUT OF NOWHERE

365
00:21:54,945 --> 00:21:56,447
AND TELL ME
THE BOTTOM'S DROPPED
OUT OF MY LIFE.

366
00:21:56,447 --> 00:21:58,449
I GOT A WEEK TO BRACE
FOR THE IMPACT.

367
00:21:58,732 --> 00:22:02,402
I'M SORRY, TONY,
THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT I AM DOING.

368
00:22:02,402 --> 00:22:04,955
YOU KNOW, THE ONLY THING
I DON'T UNDERSTAND,

369
00:22:05,456 --> 00:22:07,458
HOW COME IT TOOK YOU GUYS
TWO YEARS TO TELL ME THIS.

370
00:22:07,574 --> 00:22:09,960
LEWIS NEVER MENTIONED
THE TWO OF YOU,

371
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,962
NOT WHEN
HE WAS CONVICTED
TWO YEARS AGO,

372
00:22:11,962 --> 00:22:14,465
NOT WHEN HE WAS
SENTENCED TO DEATH
10 MONTHS AGO.

373
00:22:14,465 --> 00:22:17,468
IT WAS ONLY LAST WEEK
WHEN HIS FINAL PARDON
APPEAL WAS REJECTED.

374
00:22:17,634 --> 00:22:19,470
I FOUND
A DETECTIVE.

375
00:22:19,470 --> 00:22:21,472
THE SECOND
HE FOUND YOU,
HERE I AM.

376
00:22:25,976 --> 00:22:29,980
YOU GOTTA UNDERSTAND,
THIS ISN'T JUST
ABOUT ME, ALL RIGHT?

377
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:32,483
I MEAN, LIKE ANYBODY,
I HAVE A LOT OF
RESPONSIBILITIES.

378
00:22:32,483 --> 00:22:35,486
I'M ENGAGED.
I HAVE A FIANCEE.

379
00:22:35,486 --> 00:22:36,987
I WANT TO
START A FAMILY.

380
00:22:38,989 --> 00:22:41,492
A FAMILY'S WONDERFUL.

381
00:22:41,492 --> 00:22:43,494
LEWIS WOULD LIKE TO
HAVE KIDS, TOO.

382
00:22:43,777 --> 00:22:47,498
IF YOU CAN
POSTPONE HAVING YOURS
FOR A FEW YEARS,

383
00:22:47,498 --> 00:22:49,500
HE'LL BE ABLE TO
HAVE THAT CHANCE.

384
00:22:50,834 --> 00:22:52,503
I'M STAYING
AT THE STANHOPE.

385
00:22:52,503 --> 00:22:54,505
COULD YOU CALL
ME THERE TONIGHT?

386
00:22:54,671 --> 00:22:57,508
ALL RIGHT, I WILL.

387
00:22:57,508 --> 00:22:59,009
THANKS.
THANKS, TONY.

388
00:23:26,403 --> 00:23:28,905
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

389
00:23:31,408 --> 00:23:32,409
THIS IS BETH.

390
00:23:32,909 --> 00:23:34,911
MISS EASTERN, HI,
IT'S TONY CROFT.

391
00:23:34,911 --> 00:23:36,379
TONY, HI.

392
00:23:36,463 --> 00:23:39,916
LISTEN, KERRIE AND I
TALKED THIS OVER,

393
00:23:39,916 --> 00:23:41,418
AND WE WANT TO, UM...

394
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,922
WELL, I WANT TO--
FIRST OF ALL, SIMPLY,
I WANT TO SAY THAT,

395
00:23:46,306 --> 00:23:49,426
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

396
00:23:49,893 --> 00:23:54,314
THERE IS NO WAY IN HELL
THAT I'LL DO THE 6 YEARS.

397
00:23:55,432 --> 00:23:58,902
BUT IF SHERIFF AGREES
TO GO BACK...

398
00:24:00,437 --> 00:24:02,939
UM, WELL, THAT'S ANOTHER...

399
00:24:06,192 --> 00:24:08,445
IN THAT CASE, UM...

400
00:24:08,445 --> 00:24:11,698
YOU KNOW, IT WOULD BE
PRETTY HARD TO SAY NO.

401
00:24:13,950 --> 00:24:17,954
UH, OK. WHAT YOU'VE SAID
HAS BEEN VERY CLEAR.

402
00:24:17,954 --> 00:24:19,956
I'M ABOUT TO
GO HAVE DINNER WITH
SHERIFF RIGHT NOW,

403
00:24:19,956 --> 00:24:21,458
I'LL CALL YOU IN THE MORNING
AND TELL YOU WHAT WAS SAID.

404
00:24:21,958 --> 00:24:23,960
ALL RIGHT,
I'LL TALK TO YOU THEN.

405
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:24,961
THANK YOU, TONY.

406
00:24:24,961 --> 00:24:26,463
GOOD NIGHT.

407
00:24:47,450 --> 00:24:48,952
HEY.

408
00:24:48,952 --> 00:24:49,953
HI.

409
00:24:50,453 --> 00:24:51,454
SURPRISED I SHOWED?

410
00:24:51,955 --> 00:24:53,957
NO. WHY?

411
00:24:53,957 --> 00:24:54,958
BECAUSE I AM.

412
00:24:54,958 --> 00:24:55,959
EASTERN PARTY?

413
00:24:55,959 --> 00:24:57,460
UH, YEAH.

414
00:24:57,460 --> 00:24:58,962
RIGHT THIS WAY.

415
00:25:02,465 --> 00:25:03,967
THANKS.

416
00:25:05,468 --> 00:25:07,470
Waitress:
WOULD YOU CARE
FOR A COCKTAIL?

417
00:25:07,587 --> 00:25:10,473
GLASS OF HOUSE RED.

418
00:25:10,473 --> 00:25:11,975
YEAH, I'LL HAVE
A RUM AND COKE, PLEASE.

419
00:25:12,425 --> 00:25:13,977
THANK YOU.

420
00:25:13,977 --> 00:25:17,981
REMINDS ME OF MALAYSIA,
RUM AND COKE.

421
00:25:17,981 --> 00:25:20,483
SO, HAVE YOU SPOKEN
TO TONY?

422
00:25:20,984 --> 00:25:23,486
YES, I DID. MM-HMM.

423
00:25:25,488 --> 00:25:27,490
TONY SAID HE WAS
GOING TO GO BACK.

424
00:25:27,574 --> 00:25:29,993
YOU KNOW, TONY TOLD ME
HE WAS GOING TO CALL ME

425
00:25:29,993 --> 00:25:33,496
WHEN WE GOT BACK
FROM PANANG, SO...

426
00:25:33,613 --> 00:25:34,998
SO WHAT ARE
YOU SAYING?

427
00:25:34,998 --> 00:25:36,499
I CAN'T COUNT
ON TONY'S WORD?

428
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:39,002
NO, I'M NOT SAYING THAT.
NOT AT ALL.

429
00:25:39,002 --> 00:25:42,005
JUST, UH, I THINK IT'S GOOD
TONY SAYS HE'S GOING BACK.

430
00:25:42,171 --> 00:25:45,008
HOW COME?

431
00:25:46,459 --> 00:25:47,460
BECAUSE I'M--

432
00:25:47,794 --> 00:25:49,462
Waitress:
EXCUSE ME,
YOUR DRINKS.

433
00:25:50,597 --> 00:25:51,965
THANKS.

434
00:25:51,965 --> 00:25:52,966
THANKS A LOT.

435
00:25:54,968 --> 00:25:57,887
TONY'S ONLY GOING BACK
IF YOU'RE GOING BACK.

436
00:25:58,972 --> 00:26:00,473
YOU DIDN'T SAY THAT.

437
00:26:00,974 --> 00:26:02,475
WELL, YOU DIDN'T
LET ME FINISH.

438
00:26:02,475 --> 00:26:04,477
WELL, OK,
PLEASE FINISH,
THEN, BETH,

439
00:26:04,477 --> 00:26:07,030
FINISH WHAT
YOU'RE GONNA SAY.

440
00:26:10,984 --> 00:26:13,987
I DON'T EXPECT
YOU TO DO THIS...

441
00:26:14,487 --> 00:26:16,489
WITHOUT SOME
SORT OF COMPENSATION.

442
00:26:16,573 --> 00:26:19,492
BOTH OF LEWIS' PARENTS
HAVE PASSED ON.

443
00:26:19,492 --> 00:26:21,995
THEY LEFT
A LITTLE SOMETHING.

444
00:26:22,328 --> 00:26:25,498
HOW DOES $50,000 SOUND?

445
00:26:25,665 --> 00:26:29,586
$50,000?
THAT SOUNDS FINE,
JUST FINE...

446
00:26:31,004 --> 00:26:35,008
BUT FOR EACH YEAR.
$50,000 A YEAR.

447
00:26:35,425 --> 00:26:38,011
YOU WANT ME
TO PAY YOU $150,000

448
00:26:38,011 --> 00:26:40,513
FOR ASSUMING WHAT IS,
IN FACT,

449
00:26:40,513 --> 00:26:41,514
YOUR SHARE
OF THE RESPONSIBILITY.

450
00:26:42,015 --> 00:26:43,516
NO, NO, NO.
NOT YOU.

451
00:26:44,017 --> 00:26:45,018
LEWIS'S ESTATE.

452
00:26:45,351 --> 00:26:47,020
I MEAN, THEY GOT
HEAVY MONEY RIGHT?

453
00:26:47,020 --> 00:26:48,521
COME ON, LET'S FACE IT.

454
00:26:48,688 --> 00:26:51,024
YOU COME TO NEW YORK
ON WHAT'S PRETTY MUCH
A FISHING EXPEDITION.

455
00:26:51,024 --> 00:26:54,027
YOU STAY ON THE PARK,
EAT HERE, NOT AT SOME
CHEAP COFFEE SHOP ON LEX.

456
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:56,029
ALL RIGHT.

457
00:26:56,496 --> 00:27:00,083
SO I WILL
DRAW UP THE DRAFT
AGREEMENT TOMORROW.

458
00:27:00,083 --> 00:27:04,504
IF YOU PROMISE ME
RIGHT NOW THAT YOU'RE
GOING TO GO BACK.

459
00:27:06,039 --> 00:27:08,541
YOU KNOW WHAT'S
FUNNY TO ME...

460
00:27:08,541 --> 00:27:11,044
REALLY FUNNY?

461
00:27:11,544 --> 00:27:12,545
IS HOW PEOPLE
LIKE YOURSELF

462
00:27:12,545 --> 00:27:15,048
THINK YOU CAN JUST
BUY PEOPLE LIKE ME.

463
00:27:15,048 --> 00:27:16,516
BUT GUESS WHAT, BETH.

464
00:27:16,516 --> 00:27:19,052
I WOULDN'T WALK
INTO YOUR SHIT STORM
FOR ANY PRICE,

465
00:27:19,052 --> 00:27:20,553
AND ANY SLIM CHANCE
THAT THERE MIGHT HAVE BEEN
THAT I WOULD GO BACK

466
00:27:21,054 --> 00:27:22,855
JUST WENT BYE-BYE WHEN
YOU TRIED TO PAY ME OFF.

467
00:27:22,855 --> 00:27:24,023
Waitress:
MENUS?

468
00:27:24,474 --> 00:27:26,526
