A REALLY BIG WEEK.

594
00:33:27,169 --> 00:33:30,673
BETH, I CAN MAKE MIRACLES
HAPPEN IN A WEEK.

595
00:33:30,673 --> 00:33:32,174
DON'T DO THIS.

596
00:33:33,175 --> 00:33:35,177
DON'T DO IT.

597
