WHY DON'T YOU JUST--

598
00:33:36,679 --> 00:33:37,680
WHAT?!
I'M SORRY.

599
00:33:37,896 --> 00:33:39,181
JESUS CHRIST!

600
00:33:39,181 --> 00:33:41,183
I'M SORRY.
I'M...VERY SORRY.

601
00:33:41,684 --> 00:33:42,651
JUST...

602
00:33:48,691 --> 00:33:50,776
COULD I HAVE THAT,
PLEASE?

603
00:33:53,195 --> 00:33:54,697
IS HE BOYISH?

604
00:33:54,697 --> 00:33:55,698
WHAT?

605
00:33:56,031 --> 00:33:57,199
IS HE CUTE?

606
00:33:57,199 --> 00:33:59,201
IS HE CLEAN-CUT?
BECAUSE IF HE IS,

607
00:33:59,368 --> 00:34:00,703
AND I PUT HIM ON
THE FRONT PAGE
OF MY NEWS--

608
00:34:00,703 --> 00:34:02,204
GIVE ME SOME TIME.

609
00:34:03,706 --> 00:34:06,208
GIVE ME SOME TIME,
SOME SPACE,

610
00:34:06,709 --> 00:34:09,211
AND I'LL GIVE YOU
YOUR STORY.

611
00:34:13,716 --> 00:34:15,217
WHEN?

612
00:34:16,301 --> 00:34:17,720
SOON.

613
00:34:21,724 --> 00:34:24,226
