WHAT'S HAPPENING
HERE, BETH?

1157
01:04:38,454 --> 01:04:41,407
YOU TELL ME, SHERIFF.

1158
01:04:41,657 --> 01:04:45,411
I'M NOT SURE,
BUT I KNOW THAT
I JUST...

1159
01:04:45,411 --> 01:04:47,913
I CAN'T TAKE THIS
ANYMORE.

1160
01:04:49,415 --> 01:04:51,917
SO DON'T TAKE IT.

1161
01:04:57,723 --> 01:05:00,426
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

1162
01:05:07,433 --> 01:05:10,436
OH, MY GOD.

1163
01:05:20,329 --> 01:05:21,914
YOU'RE KILLING ME,
BETH.

1164
01:05:22,281 --> 01:05:25,417
I'M KILLING YOU?

1165
01:05:27,920 --> 01:05:30,672
YOU'RE KILLING ME.

1166
01:06:33,485 --> 01:06:35,988
SHERIFF?

1167
01:06:38,490 --> 01:06:41,493
OH, SHIT.

1168
01:06:41,610 --> 01:06:43,996
SHERIFF,
ARE YOU THERE?

1169
01:06:45,998 --> 01:06:51,503
I WAS JUST GONNA SAY
THAT I HOPED THAT, UM...

1170
01:06:52,004 --> 01:06:59,011
YOU DON'T THINK
LAST NIGHT WAS ABOUT...

1171
01:06:59,011 --> 01:07:00,512
UM...

1172
01:07:01,013 --> 01:07:02,514
COULD YOU CALL ME?

1173
01:07:02,514 --> 01:07:04,516
WHEN YOU GET THIS MESSAGE?
THAT'D BE GOOD.

1174
01:07:05,017 --> 01:07:06,518
ALL RIGHT.

1175
01:07:20,532 --> 01:07:23,035
CAN I SIT NEXT TO YOU
ON THE PLANE?

1176
01:07:46,058 --> 01:07:48,560
[PLANE TAKING OFF]

1177
01:08:06,578 --> 01:08:11,083
Beth: HEY, TONY.
TONY?

1178
01:08:11,166 --> 01:08:13,201
YOU ALL RIGHT?

1179
01:08:14,586 --> 01:08:16,588
YEAH. YEAH,
I'M FINE.

1180
01:08:16,588 --> 01:08:18,090
YOU SURE?

1181
01:08:20,042 --> 01:08:21,593
YOU WANNA, UM...

1182
01:08:21,593 --> 01:08:23,095
DO YOU WANNA
SWITCH WITH US?

1183
01:08:23,595 --> 01:08:25,097
YEAH, TONY, YOU WANT
TO SWITCH SEATS
OR SOMETHING?

1184
01:08:25,213 --> 01:08:26,098
NO, NO. YOU KNOW...

1185
01:08:26,098 --> 01:08:28,600
I LIKE MY SEAT.
IT'S FINE.

1186
01:08:28,600 --> 01:08:30,102
SHERIFF,
I'M A BIG BOY.

1187
01:08:30,102 --> 01:08:32,604
I DON'T NEED SOMEBODY
TO HOLD MY HAND, OK?

1188
01:08:33,055 --> 01:08:34,606
OK.

1189
01:08:36,608 --> 01:08:40,112
AT LEAST TILL WE GET OVER
THE PHILIPPINES.

1190
01:09:35,033 --> 01:09:36,535
Man: LET'S GO!

1191
01:09:36,535 --> 01:09:38,537
WHOO! LOOK OUT!

1192
01:09:38,837 --> 01:09:41,540
WA-HOO!

1193
01:10:11,570 --> 01:10:13,572
WE SHOULD ALL
WASH UP.

1194
01:10:13,572 --> 01:10:15,574
MEET, LIKE,
IN A HALF-HOUR
OR SOMETHING.

1195
01:10:15,574 --> 01:10:18,076
Tony:
FINE WITH ME.

1196
01:10:19,578 --> 01:10:20,579
IS THAT COOL
WITH EVERYONE?

1197
01:10:20,579 --> 01:10:21,580
SURE.

1198
01:10:21,580 --> 01:10:22,831
COOL.

1199
01:10:23,582 --> 01:10:24,583
I'M RIGHT HERE.

1200
01:10:24,583 --> 01:10:26,084
ALL RIGHT, MAN.

1201
01:11:22,223 --> 01:11:24,442
HI.

1202
01:12:22,500 --> 01:12:25,503
SHERIFF...

1203
01:12:30,007 --> 01:12:32,510
WHAT'S WRONG?

1204
01:12:32,510 --> 01:12:35,012
WHAT'S WRONG?

1205
01:12:37,014 --> 01:12:39,517
UM...

1206
01:12:39,934 --> 01:12:41,519
WHAT?

1207
01:12:43,020 --> 01:12:45,439
I'M GONNA MISS YOU.

1208
01:12:46,524 --> 01:12:49,026
I'M GONNA MISS YOU.

1209
01:13:27,097 --> 01:13:29,567
[MEN SPEAKING MALAY]

1210
01:13:38,576 --> 01:13:40,578
HE WON'T BEND.

1211
01:13:40,578 --> 01:13:43,080
ONLY ONE VISITOR
ALLOWED IN THERE.

1212
01:13:43,080 --> 01:13:44,582
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
ONE AT A TIME
OR WHAT?

1213
01:13:45,082 --> 01:13:46,584
NO, NO.
ONLY ONE TODAY.

1214
01:13:46,584 --> 01:13:48,586
OH, GREAT.
THAT'S GREAT.

1215
01:13:48,586 --> 01:13:50,087
WHAT DO YOU
WANT TO DO?

1216
01:13:50,087 --> 01:13:52,089
DO YOU MIND IF
I GO BACK THERE,
TONY, AND SEE HIM?

1217
01:13:52,339 --> 01:13:53,591
NO, NO.

1218
01:13:53,591 --> 01:13:55,092
ARE YOU SURE
ABOUT HIS?

1219
01:13:55,092 --> 01:13:57,094
YEAH, YOU GO.
GO AHEAD.

1220
01:13:58,596 --> 01:14:00,097
TELL HIM
I'LL SEE HIM SOON.

1221
01:14:00,547 --> 01:14:02,583
OK.

1222
01:14:03,601 --> 01:14:05,052
OK, COME
BACK HERE.

1223
01:14:05,552 --> 01:14:07,554
[MEN SPEAKING MALAY]

1224
01:14:07,554 --> 01:14:09,723
[UNLOCKS DOOR]

1225
01:14:22,069 --> 01:14:24,571
[SPEAKS MALAY]

1226
01:15:22,129 --> 01:15:23,630
[SPEAKS MALAY]

1227
01:15:23,630 --> 01:15:25,132
YEAH, I HEAR YOU.

1228
01:15:33,140 --> 01:15:35,642
[MAN COUGHING]

1229
01:16:17,101 --> 01:16:19,103
LEW?

1230
01:16:20,938 --> 01:16:23,107
[WEAK MUMBLING]

1231
01:16:29,163 --> 01:16:30,614
LEWIS?

1232
01:16:37,121 --> 01:16:38,122
SHERIFF?

1233
01:16:38,122 --> 01:16:39,173
YEAH.

1234
01:16:41,125 --> 01:16:43,127
DIDN'T THEY TELL YOU
I WAS COMING?

1235
01:16:43,293 --> 01:16:44,628
I WAS PRAYING.

1236
01:16:44,628 --> 01:16:47,631
I...THOUGHT YOU WERE
A DREAM 'CAUSE...

1237
01:16:47,631 --> 01:16:50,634
NO PRAYER OF
MINE HAS EVER BEEN
ANSWERED HERE BEFORE.

1238
01:16:50,968 --> 01:16:53,604
YEAH? I SURE AS HELL
AIN'T A DREAM, I'LL
TELL YOU THAT.

1239
01:16:55,139 --> 01:16:57,141
IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU.

1240
01:16:57,391 --> 01:16:58,142
IT'S GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

1241
01:16:58,142 --> 01:17:00,644
[CRYING]
YOU, TOO.

1242
01:17:00,644 --> 01:17:02,646
HOW ARE YOU, MAN?

1243
01:17:02,646 --> 01:17:04,148
I'M BETTER NOW.

1244
01:17:04,148 --> 01:17:07,651
THAT'S GOOD.
THAT'S GOOD. YEAH.

1245
01:17:07,651 --> 01:17:09,153
HOW ARE YOU?

1246
01:17:09,153 --> 01:17:10,654
I'M ALL RIGHT, MAN.

1247
01:17:10,654 --> 01:17:12,156
YOU LOOK GOOD.
NICE, NICE.

1248
01:17:12,456 --> 01:17:13,657
SPIFF-ON.

1249
01:17:13,657 --> 01:17:15,159
YEAH.

1250
01:17:15,409 --> 01:17:17,661
YOU'VE COME SO FAR.
ARE YOU THIRSTY
AT ALL?

1251
01:17:17,661 --> 01:17:18,662
DO YOU--YOU WANT
SOME TEA?

1252
01:17:19,163 --> 01:17:20,164
I CAN MAKE SOME TEA.

1253
01:17:20,631 --> 01:17:23,167
ALL RIGHT, YEAH.
LET'S HAVE SOME TEA.

1254
01:17:23,167 --> 01:17:25,169
OK. IT'S NOT WARM
OR ANYTHING, BUT--

1255
01:17:25,169 --> 01:17:26,170
THAT'S OK.

1256
01:17:26,170 --> 01:17:28,172
YEAH?

1257
01:17:30,674 --> 01:17:33,177
YOU'RE NOT COLD,
ARE YOU?

1258
01:17:33,177 --> 01:17:34,678
NO, I'M NOT COLD.

1259
01:17:34,678 --> 01:17:35,679
NO?

1260
01:17:35,679 --> 01:17:37,681
TONY IS HERE
TO SEE YOU, TOO.

1261
01:17:37,681 --> 01:17:38,682
HE'S OUTSIDE.

1262
01:17:39,183 --> 01:17:40,684
YOU SEE, THEY...

1263
01:17:40,684 --> 01:17:43,687
THEY TOOK AWAY
MY BLANKET THERE.

1264
01:17:44,188 --> 01:17:45,689
WHY'D THEY TAKE
YOUR BLANKET AWAY?

1265
01:17:45,689 --> 01:17:47,191
'CAUSE THEY WERE
SCARED THAT I WAS

1266
01:17:47,191 --> 01:17:50,194
GONNA TEAR IT
INTO STRIPS
AND HANG MYSELF.

1267
01:17:50,194 --> 01:17:51,695
SO I SAID,
"HEY, GUYS,

1268
01:17:51,695 --> 01:17:53,197
WHAT DO YOU THINK
I'M PAYING YOU FOR?"

1269
01:17:53,197 --> 01:17:54,198
[LAUGHTER]

1270
01:17:54,198 --> 01:17:55,699
[COUGHING]

1271
01:17:55,699 --> 01:17:57,701
YEAH...

1272
01:18:00,120 --> 01:18:02,706
THANK YOU, MAN.
THAT'S GOOD TEA.

1273
01:18:04,208 --> 01:18:07,711
I KNOW WHY TONY
DIDN'T COME IN HERE.

1274
01:18:07,711 --> 01:18:12,216
I KNOW 'CAUSE
THERE'S NO GOD
IN HERE.

1275
01:18:12,432 --> 01:18:13,717
THEY ONLY LET ONE VISITOR
AT A TIME HERE.

1276
01:18:14,218 --> 01:18:17,721
YOU SEE, THAT'S WHY
I PRAY NOW, SHERIFF.

1277
01:18:17,721 --> 01:18:21,725
BECAUSE...OUT THERE,

1278
01:18:21,725 --> 01:18:25,229
THERE'S...THERE'S
NO NEED TO--TO PRAY

1279
01:18:25,229 --> 01:18:29,733
WHERE GOD'S HAND
IS FELT.

1280
01:18:29,733 --> 01:18:31,235
YOU KNOW?

1281
01:18:31,618 --> 01:18:36,240
WHERE GOD IS--
IS APPARENT?

1282
01:18:36,323 --> 01:18:39,710
BUT IN HERE, THERE'S
DEFINITELY A NEED

1283
01:18:39,710 --> 01:18:44,214
T-T-TO PRAY,
TO BEG, TO PLEAD,

1284
01:18:44,214 --> 01:18:46,216
TO SING FOR...

1285
01:18:46,717 --> 01:18:48,719
FOR A SIGN LIKE...

1286
01:18:50,220 --> 01:18:55,726
YOU KNOW HOW...
HOW YOUR VOICE

1287
01:18:55,726 --> 01:19:01,181
SOUNDS SO PRETTY
IN THE SHOWER?

1288
01:19:01,181 --> 01:19:05,102
BECAUSE--BECAUSE
THERE'S NOTHING
ELSE THERE.

1289
01:19:05,102 --> 01:19:09,106
BECAUSE IT ECHOES
OFF THE WALLS, AND
IT SOUNDS PRETTY.

1290
01:19:10,607 --> 01:19:15,095
MY PRAYERS
SOUND SO PERFECT
IN HERE...

1291
01:19:15,095 --> 01:19:17,581
BECAUSE IT'S SO...

1292
01:19:17,581 --> 01:19:20,083
BECAUSE IT'S SO
TOTALLY EMPTY.

1293
01:19:20,083 --> 01:19:23,537
BECAUSE IT'S SO--
IT'S SO GODLESS.

1294
01:19:23,537 --> 01:19:27,507
IT'S SO VOID OF--
OF--OF--

1295
01:19:27,507 --> 01:19:29,509
ANYTHING.

1296
01:19:31,011 --> 01:19:34,014
DO YOU KNOW HOW
I KNOW, SHERIFF?

1297
01:19:34,514 --> 01:19:36,016
DO YOU KNOW HOW
I KNOW?

1298
01:19:36,516 --> 01:19:39,987
I KNOW BECAUSE--
BECAUSE...

1299
01:19:39,987 --> 01:19:42,990
I ASKED MYSELF

1300
01:19:42,990 --> 01:19:47,978
WOULD I COME BACK
FOR YOU?

1301
01:19:48,312 --> 01:19:53,450
AND THE ONLY ANSWER
IS A GODLESS, EMPTY,
EVIL...

1302
01:19:53,450 --> 01:19:55,802
NO.

1303
01:19:56,286 --> 01:19:59,790
I SAID I WOULDN'T
HAVE COME BACK.

1304
01:20:00,791 --> 01:20:02,292
I'M SORRY.

1305
01:20:02,292 --> 01:20:04,294
DON'T BE SORRY.
IT'S OK.

1306
01:20:04,544 --> 01:20:08,799
BECAUSE I DIDN'T
COME BACK JUST FOR YOU.

1307
01:20:08,799 --> 01:20:12,302
I DIDN'T COME BACK
JUST FOR YOU, YOU KNOW?

1308
01:20:12,803 --> 01:20:14,304
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

1309
01:20:14,304 --> 01:20:15,806
HEY, MAN, IT'S OK.

1310
01:20:15,972 --> 01:20:18,308
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

1311
01:20:18,308 --> 01:20:19,810
COME HERE. IT'S OK.

1312
01:20:19,810 --> 01:20:21,311
[CRIES]

1313
01:20:21,395 --> 01:20:22,813
IT'S OK.

1314
01:20:25,315 --> 01:20:26,316
[SHOUTS IN MALAY]

1315
01:20:26,516 --> 01:20:27,818
[RAPS ON BARS]

1316
01:20:29,820 --> 01:20:31,321
OK, MAN.

1317
01:20:32,823 --> 01:20:34,825
OK.

1318
01:20:35,325 --> 01:20:37,327
I'M GONNA SEE YOU
IN A COUPLE HOURS.

1319
01:20:37,327 --> 01:20:39,830
ALL RIGHT? ALL RIGHT?

1320
01:20:40,330 --> 01:20:42,833
THANKS FOR THE TEA,
I LIKED IT.

1321
01:20:42,833 --> 01:20:44,334
SEE YOU IN
A COUPLE HOURS, MAN.

1322
01:20:44,334 --> 01:20:46,336
YOU'LL BE
CLEANED UP GOOD.

1323
01:20:50,340 --> 01:20:52,292
SHERIFF?

1324
01:20:53,343 --> 01:20:55,679
YEAH?

1325
01:20:57,347 --> 01:21:00,350
I KNEW YOU'D COME BACK,

1326
01:21:00,350 --> 01:21:02,552
EVEN IF YOU DIDN'T.

1327
01:21:07,357 --> 01:21:09,359
THANK YOU.

1328
01:21:33,383 --> 01:21:36,386
Tony: SO HOW BAD
WAS IT?

1329
01:21:40,390 --> 01:21:42,893
I DON'T KNOW.
IT'S LIKE...

1330
01:21:42,893 --> 01:21:45,896
YOU WANNA KNOW
HOW BAD IT WAS,
IT WAS...NOT GOOD.

1331
01:21:46,146 --> 01:21:48,899
WHAT WASN'T GOOD?
THE PRISON OR LEWIS?
WHICH ONE?

1332
01:21:49,232 --> 01:21:51,902
THE PRISON SUCKS FOR SURE.

1333
01:21:51,902 --> 01:21:53,904
IT'S DIRTY, IT'S SCARY,
IT'S THIRD WORLD.

1334
01:21:53,904 --> 01:21:56,857
HOW'S LEWIS?
IS HE SICK?

1335
01:21:56,940 --> 01:21:58,408
IS HE ALL THERE
MENTALLY?

1336
01:21:58,408 --> 01:22:00,410
IS HE THE SAME GUY
WE USED TO KNOW?

1337
01:22:00,527 --> 01:22:02,412
I DON'T THINK HE'S LOST
HIS MIND OR ANYTHING,

1338
01:22:02,412 --> 01:22:05,415
BUT IT'S NOT EASY SITTING
AROUND A PRISON CELL
WAITING TO HANG.

1339
01:22:05,916 --> 01:22:09,419
WHAT DID HE SAY?
DID HE TELL YOU
ANYTHING?

1340
01:22:09,870 --> 01:22:11,922
HE JUST BABBLED
A LITTLE BIT, TONY.

1341
01:22:11,922 --> 01:22:14,424
YOU KNOW, LIKE,
RAMBLED A LITTLE BIT.

1342
01:22:14,424 --> 01:22:15,425
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

1343
01:22:15,509 --> 01:22:17,427
LIKE STREAM-OF-
CONSCIOUSNESS STUFF.

1344
01:22:17,427 --> 01:22:21,381
GOD'S NOT IN HERE,
THERE'S NO GOD IN HERE.

1345
01:22:21,465 --> 01:22:23,934
IT SOUNDS BEAUTIFUL IN HERE,
LIKE, WHEN YOU SING
IN THE SHOWER, JUST--

1346
01:22:24,434 --> 01:22:26,937
SO BASICALLY, YOU'RE
SAYING HE LOST IT.

1347
01:22:27,020 --> 01:22:29,439
HE'S HANGING ON
TO ANYTHING HE
POSSIBLY CAN, TONY.

1348
01:22:29,689 --> 01:22:31,942
LOOK, NO ONE'S
QUESTIONING
HIS COURAGE--

1349
01:22:32,108 --> 01:22:32,943
YOU'RE QUESTIONING
HIS SANITY.

1350
01:22:32,943 --> 01:22:34,444
YOU WANT A WAY OUT,
FIND A WAY OUT,

1351
01:22:34,444 --> 01:22:38,732
BUT DON'T MAKE THIS
ABOUT LEWIS. HE'S
ALWAYS TALKED THAT WAY.

1352
01:22:41,201 --> 01:22:43,954
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
ALWAYS?

1353
01:22:44,237 --> 01:22:46,456
YOU'RE
ONLY HIS LAWYER.

1354
01:22:46,456 --> 01:22:48,458
YOU'VE KNOWN HIM
FOR 2 YEARS.

1355
01:22:51,962 --> 01:22:53,797
24 YEARS.

1356
01:22:56,967 --> 01:22:59,419
I'M HIS SISTER.

1357
01:23:00,470 --> 01:23:01,471
WHAT?

1358
01:23:07,928 --> 01:23:09,980
HE'S MY BABY BROTHER.

1359
01:23:35,371 --> 01:23:37,373
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

1360
01:23:39,876 --> 01:23:42,378
I THOUGHT YOU WOULDN'T
TRUST ME, SHERIFF.

1361
01:23:44,380 --> 01:23:46,883
I THOUGHT YOU'D THINK
I'D DO ANYTHING,
THAT I'D...

1362
01:23:46,883 --> 01:23:51,387
SAY ANYTHING,
THAT I'D SELL YOU OUT,
THAT I'D...

1363
01:23:52,889 --> 01:23:54,891
I WANTED TO.
I WANTED TO TELL YOU.

1364
01:23:54,891 --> 01:23:56,859
I TR-TRIED TO TELL YOU.

1365
01:23:58,394 --> 01:24:00,396
BUT YOUDIDN'T
TELL ME.

1366
01:24:01,397 --> 01:24:04,400
[WHISPERS]
But you didn't
tell me.

1367
01:24:31,928 --> 01:24:33,646
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

1368
01:24:34,430 --> 01:24:35,932
SHERIFF?

1369
01:24:43,239 --> 01:24:44,440
[DOOR CLOSES]

1370
01:24:46,275 --> 01:24:49,278
WHAT ARE WE
STILL DOING HERE?

1371
01:24:49,946 --> 01:24:52,448
I WISH IT WAS
THAT SIMPLE, TONY.

1372
01:24:52,832 --> 01:24:53,950
I THINK
IT'S THAT SIMPLE.

1373
01:24:54,450 --> 01:24:55,952
YOU KNOW,
I CAME BACK HERE.

1374
01:24:55,952 --> 01:24:57,954
I CAME BACK HERE
BASED ON WHAT
SHE TOLD ME, OK?

1375
01:24:58,454 --> 01:25:00,790
SHE GAVE ME HER WORD,
AND SHE LIED.

1376
01:25:03,459 --> 01:25:05,928
HOW ARE WE GONNA
TRUST HER, SHERIFF?

1377
01:25:07,964 --> 01:25:10,967
SHERIFF...LOOK,
SHE DRAGS US INTO
THIS NIGHTMARE, OK?

1378
01:25:10,967 --> 01:25:14,220
WE FIND OUT IT IS
HER OWN PERSONAL NIGHTMARE,

1379
01:25:14,220 --> 01:25:16,472
A WOMAN WE DON'T KNOW
FROM ADAM, YOU KNOW?

1380
01:25:16,472 --> 01:25:18,474
I DON'T KNOW HER,
YOU DON'T KNOW HER.

1381
01:25:18,858 --> 01:25:20,476
WHAT?

1382
01:25:20,643 --> 01:25:22,478
I KNOW HER.

1383
01:25:23,980 --> 01:25:26,198
LIKE,KNOWHER.

1384
01:25:28,484 --> 01:25:30,486
DON'T...
DON'T EVEN...DON'T.

1385
01:25:30,653 --> 01:25:33,239
FUCK. FUCK.

1386
01:25:34,490 --> 01:25:37,493
ALL RIGHT,
I'M AN ASSHOLE.

1387
01:25:37,660 --> 01:25:39,495
NO, TONY.

1388
01:25:39,495 --> 01:25:41,998
THIS TIME,I'M
THE FUCKIN' ASSHOLE.

1389
01:25:41,998 --> 01:25:44,500
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

1390
01:25:44,667 --> 01:25:47,003
WHAT THE FUCK DO
I OWE YOU TO TELL YOU
SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

1391
01:25:47,003 --> 01:25:49,005
IT'S NOT LIKE
IT'S BEEN GOING ON
FOREVER, ALL RIGHT?

1392
01:25:49,388 --> 01:25:51,007
IT HAPPENED.

1393
01:25:51,257 --> 01:25:52,508
YOU LISTEN TO ME.

1394
01:25:52,508 --> 01:25:54,510
DON'T EVEN TRY
TO MAKE IT LIKE
I'M HOLDING OUT ON YOU,

1395
01:25:54,510 --> 01:25:56,012
BECAUSE I SWEAR TO GOD
I'M NOT HOLDING
SHIT OUT ON YOU.

1396
01:25:56,512 --> 01:25:57,513
ALL RIGHT.

1397
01:25:58,014 --> 01:25:59,015
LISTEN TO ME, SHERIFF.

1398
01:25:59,515 --> 01:26:01,017
THIS GIRL
WILL DO ANYTHING

1399
01:26:01,517 --> 01:26:05,021
TO GET YOU TO DO
WHAT SHE NEEDS YOU TO,
ALL RIGHT?

1400
01:26:05,404 --> 01:26:08,024
THAT'S HER BROTHER
IN THERE--HER BLOOD.

1401
01:26:08,024 --> 01:26:10,526
SHE'LL LIE TO YOU,
SHE'LL SLEEP WITH YOU,

1402
01:26:10,659 --> 01:26:13,029
SHE'LL TELL YOU
SHE LOVES YOU,
SHE'LL DO ANYTHING.

1403
01:26:13,029 --> 01:26:15,531
SHE'LL GET DOWN ON
HER KNEES AND BEG YOU.

1404
01:26:15,531 --> 01:26:18,034
BUT DON'T BELIEVE IT.
IT'S A SETUP.

1405
01:26:18,417 --> 01:26:22,538
WE WALK OUT OF HERE,
