WE LEAVE, WE LIVE.

1407
01:26:26,042 --> 01:26:29,345
THAT'S THE ONE THING
I KNOW FOR SURE
RIGHT NOW.

1408
01:26:35,551 --> 01:26:37,053
[BETH SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

1409
01:26:40,139 --> 01:26:42,558
Beth: HUH?
DOES HE HAVE CLOTHES?

1410
01:26:42,641 --> 01:26:45,561
CAN YOU GET HIM
A SHOWER, A SHAVE,

1411
01:26:45,561 --> 01:26:48,064
BEFORE HE SHOWS UP
IN COURT?

1412
01:26:48,064 --> 01:26:49,565
UH-HUH. OK, LISTEN.

1413
01:26:49,648 --> 01:26:50,566
I--

1414
01:27:01,327 --> 01:27:04,547
[CAR DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES]

1415
01:27:22,598 --> 01:27:25,184
[CAR DOOR CLOSES]

1416
01:28:03,639 --> 01:28:06,142
Woman: WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU, SIR?

1417
01:28:06,142 --> 01:28:08,144
WE NEED TWO SEATS
ON ANY FLIGHT

1418
01:28:08,144 --> 01:28:10,729
THAT'S GONNA GET US
TO NEW YORK...
AS FAST AS POSSIBLE.

1419
01:28:28,664 --> 01:28:31,167
Tony: WHAT, SHERIFF?
WHAT IS IT?

1420
01:28:33,169 --> 01:28:35,671
I TRASHED THAT BIKE,
TONY.

1421
01:28:36,088 --> 01:28:37,673
SO FUCKIN' WHAT?

1422
01:28:37,673 --> 01:28:40,176
GET ON THE PLANE,
SHERIFF.

1423
01:28:40,259 --> 01:28:43,679
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO?
YOU WANT TO ROT IN
ONE OF THESE PRISONS?

1424
01:28:43,679 --> 01:28:46,182
I THINK I'M GONNA
TAKE MY CHANCES, TONY.

1425
01:28:46,398 --> 01:28:48,684
YOU DON'T HAVE
ANY CHANCES, SHERIFF.

1426
01:28:48,684 --> 01:28:52,188
DON'T LEAVE YOUR LIFE
TO FATE. THIS IS STUPID.

1427
01:28:52,188 --> 01:28:54,190
I DON'T KNOW, TONY.

1428
01:29:05,201 --> 01:29:07,203
YOU HAVE A SAFE FLIGHT.

1429
01:29:24,720 --> 01:29:27,357
[MAN SPEAKING MALAY]

1430
01:29:51,381 --> 01:29:52,882
WHAT'S HE SAYING?

1431
01:29:52,882 --> 01:29:54,884
HE SAYS,
"THEY RETURNED...

1432
01:29:54,884 --> 01:29:57,887
"BUT BECAME FRIGHTENED
AND MAY HAVE LEFT.

1433
01:29:57,887 --> 01:30:01,891
WHILE WE LOOK INTO THIS,
WE REQUEST ADJOURNMENT
TILL THE TWO CAN BE FOUND."

1434
01:30:02,225 --> 01:30:03,393
[JUDGE SPEAKING MALAY]

1435
01:30:07,480 --> 01:30:09,899
UM, HE'S WORRIED
ABOUT THE APPEARANCE

1436
01:30:09,899 --> 01:30:11,401
OF PREFERENTIAL
TREATMENT.

1437
01:30:13,403 --> 01:30:15,405
[JUDGE CONTINUES SPEAKING]

1438
01:30:20,660 --> 01:30:21,911
[DOOR CLOSES]

1439
01:30:27,417 --> 01:30:28,918
[WITH ACCENT]
SHERIFF.

1440
01:30:29,202 --> 01:30:30,920
[CONTINUES SPEAKING
IN MALAY]

1441
01:30:38,928 --> 01:30:40,630
[GASPS]

1442
01:30:43,433 --> 01:30:45,435
[JUDGE SPEAKING MALAY]

1443
01:30:58,948 --> 01:31:00,950
HEY, HOW ARE YOU?

1444
01:31:00,950 --> 01:31:03,953
Judge: MY FAITH IN HUMANITY
IS HALF RESTORED.

1445
01:31:04,403 --> 01:31:05,955
IN RETURNING VOLUNTARILY,

1446
01:31:05,955 --> 01:31:09,408
YOU ARE TO BE COMMENDED
FOR YOUR COURAGE.

1447
01:31:09,492 --> 01:31:11,961
IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU WISH TO SAY

1448
01:31:12,462 --> 01:31:14,330
TO THIS COURT,
MR. VOLGECHEREV?

1449
01:31:18,468 --> 01:31:19,969
NOT REALLY, YOUR HONOR.

1450
01:31:21,471 --> 01:31:23,973
JUST THAT WE WERE
YOUNG AND STUPID...

1451
01:31:24,474 --> 01:31:28,478
I GUESS, BUT NOT EVIL.

1452
01:31:28,811 --> 01:31:31,981
I DIDN'T COME BACK
HERE TODAY BECAUSE
I'M COURAGEOUS.

1453
01:31:31,981 --> 01:31:36,986
I CAME BACK HERE BECAUSE
I'VE BEEN CARELESS
FOR A VERY LONG TIME,

1454
01:31:36,986 --> 01:31:39,772
AND I'M SICK
OF THAT FEELING.

1455
01:31:40,990 --> 01:31:42,992
THE SIMPLE FACT,
YOUR HONOR,

1456
01:31:43,359 --> 01:31:45,995
IS THAT
I AM RESPONSIBLE...

1457
01:31:45,995 --> 01:31:47,997
AND I'M ALSO SCARED.

1458
01:31:50,500 --> 01:31:54,003
BUT I AM WILLING TO DO
WHATEVER'S NECESSARY...

1459
01:31:55,505 --> 01:31:58,925
IN ORDER FOR YOU TO SPARE
MY FRIEND'S LIFE.

1460
01:32:01,010 --> 01:32:02,512
[SOBBING]

1461
01:32:05,014 --> 01:32:06,516
HOW DO YOU PLEAD?

1462
01:32:06,766 --> 01:32:09,018
I'M GUILTY.

1463
01:32:09,268 --> 01:32:10,019
[CRYING]

1464
01:32:10,520 --> 01:32:11,521
Judge:
FOLLOWING THIS HEARING,

1465
01:32:11,854 --> 01:32:15,308
YOU WILL BE DETAINED
IN PANANG PRISON
TO AWAIT SENTENCE.

1466
01:32:19,028 --> 01:32:21,030
[JUDGE SPEAKING MALAY]

1467
01:32:28,871 --> 01:32:30,039
[SOBBING]

1468
01:32:30,039 --> 01:32:32,041
[ATTORNEY SPEAKING MALAY]

1469
01:32:44,420 --> 01:32:46,005
[JUDGE SPEAKING MALAY]

1470
01:32:48,007 --> 01:32:49,508
[CRYING]

1471
01:32:49,508 --> 01:32:53,145
HE ASKED THE PROSECUTOR
IF HE WILL NOW AGREE
TO REDUCE THE CHARGES.

1472
01:32:55,514 --> 01:32:57,567
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1473
01:32:59,268 --> 01:33:01,821
PROSECUTOR HAS AGREED.

1474
01:33:08,527 --> 01:33:10,029
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1475
01:33:12,031 --> 01:33:13,532
[WOMAN SPEAKS MALAY]

1476
01:33:18,254 --> 01:33:22,291
CHIEF JUSTICE
WILL BE BACK SHORTLY
WITH HIS DECISION.

1477
01:33:29,048 --> 01:33:30,549
[TIRES SQUEAL]

1478
01:33:41,560 --> 01:33:43,446
BETH?

1479
01:33:46,065 --> 01:33:48,067
WE'RE BACK IN SESSION.

1480
01:33:48,067 --> 01:33:49,068
WE'RE BACK?

1481
01:33:49,068 --> 01:33:50,069
YEAH.

1482
01:33:51,570 --> 01:33:53,572
[WOMAN SPEAKS MALAY]

1483
01:34:12,591 --> 01:34:14,093
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1484
01:34:18,064 --> 01:34:22,101
THE DEPUTY HIGH MINISTER
HAS TOLD CHIEF JUSTICE
HE IS ANGERED

1485
01:34:22,101 --> 01:34:25,604
ABOUT SOME
INTERNATIONAL NEWS STORY,
I'M NOT SURE WHAT.

1486
01:34:25,738 --> 01:34:27,106
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1487
01:34:27,606 --> 01:34:29,108
M.J. MAJOR.

1488
01:34:29,525 --> 01:34:31,610
[CONTINUES SPEAKING
IN MALAY]

1489
01:34:32,111 --> 01:34:34,580
Translator:
AN AMERICAN STORY
THAT WAS PICKED UP

1490
01:34:34,664 --> 01:34:36,115
BY THEASIAN
INTERNATIONAL TRIBUNE.

1491
01:34:36,115 --> 01:34:38,617
Judge:
"IN A COUNTRY PROUD
OF ITS MANY SPECIES

1492
01:34:38,751 --> 01:34:40,619
"OF EXOTIC BUTTERFLIES,

1493
01:34:40,619 --> 01:34:43,622
"A BUTTERFLY IS ABOUT
TO BE BROKEN ON A WHEEL.

1494
01:34:44,006 --> 01:34:47,626
"THE WHEEL IS
MALAYSIAN JUSTICE--

1495
01:34:47,626 --> 01:34:51,630
A TERM WHICH STRIKES
ONE AMERICAN WOMAN
AS A CRUEL JOKE."

1496
01:34:52,098 --> 01:34:53,132
YOUR HONOR--

1497
01:34:53,132 --> 01:34:54,633
Judge: "THE WOMAN IS
BETH McBRIDE, 28..."

1498
01:34:55,101 --> 01:34:57,636
PLEASE BELIEVE ME
WHEN I SAY I HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

1499
01:34:58,104 --> 01:35:00,139
"...ARRESTED
TWO YEARS AGO IN PANANG.

1500
01:35:00,139 --> 01:35:02,641
"BLAMED FOR HAVING
BOUGHT THE LION'S SHARE
OF HASHISH

1501
01:35:02,641 --> 01:35:04,143
"WITH TWO FRIENDS,

1502
01:35:04,443 --> 01:35:09,148
THIS NATURE-LOVING
YOUNG MAN NOW INCREDIBLY
FACES DEATH."

1503
01:35:09,615 --> 01:35:12,151
SHE WAS DETERMINED
TO WRITE THE STORY,
YOUR HONOR--

1504
01:35:12,151 --> 01:35:13,569
SILENCE!

1505
01:35:14,653 --> 01:35:17,156
WE KNOW YOU WESTERNERS
DON'T UNDERSTAND

1506
01:35:17,156 --> 01:35:18,657
OUR ATTITUDE
TOWARD DRUGS,

1507
01:35:18,657 --> 01:35:20,659
BUT WE DON'T
UNDERSTAND YOURS.

1508
01:35:20,910 --> 01:35:22,161
YOUR CITIES
ARE DECAYING.

1509
01:35:22,161 --> 01:35:25,631
THE SOULS OF
YOUR YOUNG PEOPLE
ARE STOLEN FROM YOU.

1510
01:35:25,715 --> 01:35:27,666
OUR LAWS
MAY SEEM HARSH,

1511
01:35:27,666 --> 01:35:29,668
BUT OUR STREETS
REMAIN SAFE,

1512
01:35:29,668 --> 01:35:31,670
AND OUR YOUTH
IS PROTECTED.

1513
01:35:31,670 --> 01:35:34,673
SO WHEN
AN AMERICAN JOURNALIST
TRIES TO CRITICIZE

1514
01:35:34,673 --> 01:35:36,142
OUR JUDICIAL SYSTEM--

1515
01:35:36,225 --> 01:35:37,176
I BEGGED HER NOT TO.
I BEGGED HER.

1516
01:35:37,676 --> 01:35:38,677
I DID EVERYTHING
I POSSIBLY COULD...

1517
01:35:38,677 --> 01:35:39,678
SILENCE!

1518
01:35:39,678 --> 01:35:40,679
...TO STOP HER
FROM DOING IT!

1519
01:35:41,063 --> 01:35:42,681
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1520
01:35:50,406 --> 01:35:54,193
WHAT IS IT?
WHAT IS HE SAYING?
WHAT DID HE SAY?

1521
01:36:00,366 --> 01:36:01,700
WHAT IS HE SAYING?!

1522
01:36:01,700 --> 01:36:03,702
HE WILL NOT AMEND
THE CHARGE NOW.

1523
01:36:03,702 --> 01:36:04,703
WHAT?

1524
01:36:04,703 --> 01:36:06,205
HE MUST BE HANGED TOMORROW
AS SCHEDULED.

1525
01:36:06,205 --> 01:36:07,206
WHAT--

1526
01:36:07,423 --> 01:36:09,208
[ATTORNEY SPEAKING MALAY]

1527
01:36:09,375 --> 01:36:10,709
WHAT? LEWIS--

1528
01:36:11,127 --> 01:36:12,711
[CRYING]

1529
01:36:12,711 --> 01:36:14,713
YOUR HONOR,
I CAME BACK!
YOU CAN'T HANG HIM!

1530
01:36:14,964 --> 01:36:16,215
Beth: LEWIS! LEWIS...

1531
01:36:16,215 --> 01:36:17,716
[BETH YELLING
UNINTELLIGIBLY]

1532
01:36:17,716 --> 01:36:21,220
LEWIS! LEWIS!
LEWIS, I LOVE YOU...

1533
01:36:21,437 --> 01:36:23,722
I LOVE YOU!

1534
01:36:24,223 --> 01:36:25,224
LEWIS!

1535
01:36:25,524 --> 01:36:27,726
LEWIS--GET YOUR
FUCKING HANDS OFF ME!

1536
01:36:27,860 --> 01:36:29,228
WHAT IS THE MATTER
WITH YOU PEOPLE?

1537
01:36:29,612 --> 01:36:32,231
WHAT IS THE MATTER
WITH YOU PEOPLE?!

1538
01:36:32,698 --> 01:36:34,233
[UNINTELLIGIBLE]

1539
01:36:34,233 --> 01:36:35,734
YOU MOTHERFUCKER!

1540
01:36:35,951 --> 01:36:38,237
YOU LYING
SON OF A BITCH!

1541
01:36:38,370 --> 01:36:41,740
GOD DAMN IT, SHERIFF...

1542
01:36:43,742 --> 01:36:45,744
[REPORTERS
SHOUTING QUESTIONS]

1543
01:37:17,993 --> 01:37:20,412
[MAN SINGING,
CALLING PEOPLE TO PRAYER]

1544
01:37:37,178 --> 01:37:38,513
[ALL SINGING]

1545
01:37:46,971 --> 01:37:50,475
[MAN LEADING PRAYERS
IN MALAY]

1546
01:37:50,475 --> 01:37:51,976
[PEOPLE RESPONDING]

1547
01:37:58,483 --> 01:37:59,984
[FAN WHIRRING]

1548
01:38:11,496 --> 01:38:13,498
Lewis: NO!

1549
01:38:13,998 --> 01:38:16,468
[SCREAMING IN MALAY]

1550
01:38:16,668 --> 01:38:17,469
[SOBBING]

1551
01:38:17,469 --> 01:38:19,971
I DON'T WANT TO DIE!

1552
01:38:20,088 --> 01:38:20,972
NO!

1553
01:38:20,972 --> 01:38:22,974
YOU FUCKING BASTARDS!

1554
01:38:23,224 --> 01:38:26,478
[SCREAMING IN MALAY]

1555
01:38:26,978 --> 01:38:28,480
I DON'T WANT TO DIE!

1556
01:38:28,980 --> 01:38:30,482
AAH!

1557
01:38:30,482 --> 01:38:31,483
HELP!

1558
01:38:31,733 --> 01:38:32,984
LEWIS...

1559
01:38:32,984 --> 01:38:33,985
LEWIS!

1560
01:38:34,486 --> 01:38:35,487
LEWIS!

1561
01:38:35,687 --> 01:38:37,489
[PLEADING IN MALAY]

1562
01:38:41,493 --> 01:38:42,994
[LEWIS SCREAMING]

1563
01:38:43,361 --> 01:38:46,498
DON'T DO IT!
I DON'T WANT TO DIE!

1564
01:38:46,948 --> 01:38:51,503
YOU FUCKING BASTARDS!
YOU--AAH!

1565
01:38:51,503 --> 01:38:53,505
[YELLING IN MALAY]

1566
01:38:53,505 --> 01:38:55,507
AAH!

1567
01:38:55,507 --> 01:38:58,009
DON'T...DON'T...

1568
01:38:58,093 --> 01:39:00,011
[LEWIS CONTINUES YELLING]

1569
01:39:09,521 --> 01:39:11,022
[CRYING]

1570
01:39:12,524 --> 01:39:15,026
NO! NO!

1571
01:39:19,030 --> 01:39:20,782
Lewis...

1572
01:39:22,033 --> 01:39:23,818
[SOBBING]

1573
01:39:25,036 --> 01:39:27,288
LEW! LEWIS!

1574
01:39:32,744 --> 01:39:34,045
NO! NO!

1575
01:39:34,546 --> 01:39:36,047
Sheriff: LEWIS!

1576
01:39:36,047 --> 01:39:37,048
LEWIS!

1577
01:39:37,549 --> 01:39:39,551
LEWIS! GOD DAMN IT,
LOOK UP HERE!

1578
01:39:39,551 --> 01:39:41,503
SHERIFF?!

1579
01:39:41,586 --> 01:39:44,339
I'M HERE, LEWIS!
I'M RIGHT HERE!

1580
01:39:45,557 --> 01:39:47,475
YOU'RE NOT ALONE,
LEWIS!

1581
01:39:51,813 --> 01:39:54,065
Sheriff:
LOOK AT ME, LEWIS!

1582
01:39:54,399 --> 01:39:58,570
YOU'RE NOT ALONE,
LEWIS. LOOK AT ME.
YOU'RE NOT ALONE.

1583
01:39:58,570 --> 01:40:00,572
I'M HERE. LOOK AT ME.
SEE ME, LEWIS.

1584
01:40:01,022 --> 01:40:04,576
YOU'RE NOT ALONE.
