1585
01:40:04,659 --> 01:40:07,078
I'M RIGHT HERE, LEWIS.
I'M RIGHT HERE.

1586
01:40:07,278 --> 01:40:09,581
I SEE YOU, LEWIS!
I'M RIGHT HERE!

1587
01:40:09,948 --> 01:40:13,034
LEWIS, YOU ARE NOT
