1599
01:41:12,728 --> 01:41:14,229
OK.

1600
01:41:14,229 --> 01:41:15,731
UP!

1601
01:41:15,731 --> 01:41:16,732
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1602
01:41:16,732 --> 01:41:17,733
OK.

1603
01:41:20,736 --> 01:41:22,237
WHERE AM I GOING HERE?

1604
01:41:22,738 --> 01:41:24,239
[SPEAKING MALAY]

1605
01:41:41,256 --> 01:41:42,758
[GUARD SPEAKING
INDISTINCTLY]

1606
01:42:04,229 --> 01:42:06,231
[GUARD SPEAKING MALAY]

1607
01:42:12,237 --> 01:42:14,489
Beth.

1608
01:42:24,749 --> 01:42:26,751
WERE YOU THERE?

1609
01:42:26,751 --> 01:42:28,753
Yeah.

1610
01:42:28,837 --> 01:42:31,756
HE WASN'T AFRAID, BETH.

1611
01:42:33,758 --> 01:42:36,761
HE WALKED RIGHT PAST ME,
AND THEN...

1612
01:42:36,761 --> 01:42:41,266
