TELL ME THE TRUTH.

1615
01:42:47,272 --> 01:42:50,275
IT WAS HARD.
IT WAS HARD, BUT...

1616
01:42:51,776 --> 01:42:54,279
YOU KNOW,
I THINK THAT...

1617
01:42:55,780 --> 01:43:00,785
HE FOUND AT--AT THE END,
BETH, AT THE END...

1618
01:43:02,754 --> 01:43:06,591
I MEAN, HE WAS LEWIS,
YOU KNOW?

1619
01:43:07,759 --> 01:43:10,195
AND AT THAT LAST SECOND...

1620
01:43:10,195 --> 01:43:13,682
I SWEAR TO GOD...

1621
01:43:13,882 --> 01:43:17,185
HE WAS AT PEACE
WITH EVERYTHING.

1622
01:43:17,385 --> 01:43:19,688
HE WAS.

1623
01:43:23,191 --> 01:43:26,695
I JUST WISH
I COULD'VE DONE
SOMETHING, YOU KNOW...

